Don't run "python manage.py collectstaic" otherwise error occurs.

--- On settings.py: ----------------------------------------------------
Change "SECRET_KEY = 'abcdefg'" to different secret key for secure.

Replace "EMAIL_HOST_USER = 'example@gmail.com'" with your email address.

Replase "EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD = 'example'" with your email password.
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Python 3.8.5 is recommended to use but the above versions will be fine.

If you use gmail, do 2 things below to get over very strong google's security.

1. Allow less secure apps: ON ↓↓↓ 
https://myaccount.google.com/lesssecureapps

2. Allow access to your Google account: ON (Tap "Continue") ↓↓↓
https://accounts.google.com/DisplayUnlockCaptcha
